cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS 

This paper is about using deep learning for image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a novel loss function that incorporates topological information, which is a technique that falls under the umbrella of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of persistent homology, a concept from algebraic topology, also suggests a potential connection to neural networks (cs.NE) and data structures (cs.DS).
